author: stsp
msg: Move gpg-agent behind GNOME Keyring, Kwallet, and Keychain, by default.
We don't want to disturb existing setups that use existing password
SVN__DEFAULT_AUTH_PROVIDER_LIST that expands to the default list
of auth providers (previously the list was listed twice).
Change the list to reflect the priority order described above.

msg: Fix for DIRSERVER-1635: Use the session key and right key usage to verify the checksum. Reworked the tests to be able to set the checksum to use. Note that the tests are highly coupled to the Sun Java implementation, as fields in internal classes are modified using reflection.
